channel.title: How to add Item on Interfaces? [DELTA]
channel.description:
How would you go about adding an item on an interface? For example, a net on an interface saying, the tutor gives you a net.
Thanks

item.title: How to add Item on Interfaces? [DELTA]
item.dc:creator: @Skiire Skiire
item.description:
@Skiire wrote:

Add a sprites folder in your client then in your RSInterface class do something like this:

public static void customInterface(RSFont[] TDA) {
	RSInterface Interface = addTabInterface(/*TODO*/);

}

You’ll have to build onto it, there are plenty of tutorials for custom interfaces though.
